{"tid":909247,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中六畢業生人數持續下降 VTC下學年減數百個收生學額","createTime":"2018-11-20T08:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T03:46:47.000Z","uid":166622,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6736956608ed213fe9b10afd7610fd14b97ae7cd","tid":909247,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"職業訓練局(VTC)下學年將開辦超過140個課程，提供約1.7萬個學額。為配合智能城市發展，VTC將推出多項新課程包括人工智能及手機軟件開發高級文憑、智能科技及網絡應用高級文憑等，以培育人工智能、大數據分析及網絡安全等人才。<br />\n<br />\n但VTC指出，收生人數「滑坡」幅度較中六畢業生人數下降低，但仍需要調整收生學額，減少下學年課程學額約幾百個，包括計算機科學等。<br />\n<br />\n中六畢業生人數未來持續下降，職訓局副執行幹事梁任城指，VTC每年報名人數約3萬個，本學年情況與去年相若。他指，VTC報名人數「滑坡」幅度較中六畢業生人數下降低，但仍需要調整收生學額，減少下學年課程學額約幾百個，包括計算機科學等。他指，VTC會「嚴陣以待」應對，因應市場需求及報讀情況而調整學額。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfc5713d2492aed452d0ca50dbd77b1e7523629","tid":909247,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b0bdf20e7017d202bb2dbacd64277e68a65fb0","tid":909247,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T09:02:28.000Z","msg":"計算機科學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔覺得好怪咩"},{"pid":"6830678fa7c2dfec8662ca92e12adc998165ed40","tid":909247,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T03:40:33.000Z","msg":"好在無收蝗蟲充數"},{"pid":"c5e35506063409e3c7749b292e66c204e7f1e41a","tid":909247,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T03:45:31.000Z","msg":"2022～2030年年都有大量中6生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3b77c5f61c29c99dd89bb6f4a492bcf8d65